  - llm-evaluation
  - epistemic-behavior
abstract: >-
  A sociolinguistic evaluation framework that audits reasoning honesty
  in large language models. Tests whether AI models reason transparently
  about their limitations or deploy patterned evasion strategies, and
  whether those patterns shift based on who the model believes is asking.
